# Invoice Automation (UiPath)

## 📌 Overview
This project automates **invoice data extraction** using UiPath.  
It reads invoice files, extracts details (Invoice No, Date, Vendor, Amount), and stores them in Excel.

## ⚙️ Workflow Steps
1. Load invoice PDFs from a folder.
2. Extract fields using Document Understanding + Regex.
3. Validate extracted data.
4. Store results in Excel and generate summary.

## 📊 Example Output
| Invoice No | Date       | Vendor       | Amount |
|------------|------------|--------------|--------|
| INV001     | 01-07-2024 | ABC Pvt Ltd  | 5000   |
| INV002     | 05-07-2024 | XYZ Traders  | 7500   |

## 🚀 Key Learning
- Document Understanding
- Exception handling
- Excel data writing

